        "L0": "Thinking — Raw hunches, questions, and fragments from agents and humans",
        "L1": "Structure — Assets, services, pipelines, teams, controls, and their ownership",
        "L2": "Flow — Dependencies, data flows, incident escalation, and CI/CD sequences",
        "L3": "Knowledge — Threats, vulnerabilities, findings, mitigations, and compliance mappings",
        "L4": "Prospect — Risk decisions, planned remediations, audits, and recommended actions"
    },
